StringGroups.name: Group 26
entries:
PSO is a unique game in that your character can
exist offline and online throughout your adventure.
In order to keep track of this, your character
information is tied to the Serial Number and Access
Key.
 Because of this, you must play on the same
Dreamcast throughout the entire adventure.

In order to identify your character, the PSO
server will register the time and date of your
Dreamcast. This will ensure that no one else can
use your PSO online account without your
permission. This information will not be used in
any other way, or distributed to any third party.
Because the PSO servers are a part of the game, no
personal information is collected. By pressing the
A button, you understand that this registration
process will occur.

The PSO servers are an extension of the game.
We collect the time and date of registration and
the Serial Number and Access Key. No personal
information is collected.

StringGroups.name: Group 28
entries:
Sonic Team maintains the servers for PSO Ver.2.
Using code not authorized by Sega damages
the servers. We ask that all users refrain
from using any unauthorized code.
We maintain the right to terminate access rights
to our servers. With this in mind, please try and
conduct yourself in a manner that is conducive to
everyone's enjoyment.
